dc_title_s: Insurance maps of Minneapolis, Minnesota, last revised 1930, Volume 6
dc_description_s: Updated with pasteover slips and additional sheets. Date of last revision varies between 1924-1930. Each volume includes a map of ward lines and district lines and a volume boundary map (index map to all volumes). Volume 6 includes suburban key map. For list and location of suburban towns shown in Volume Six, - see suburban key map and map of Richfield (Sheet No. 675) in that volume.|v.6: sheets 601-722|70 Centimeters|Scale 1:600. 50 feet to 1 inch|City of Minneapolis Archives
